canvases.label: Untitled--I keep thinking where we went wrong. We have no one to talk to now, however, I will not allow this loneliness to destroy me,--I STILL HAVE MY DREAMS. I would like an elegant home, a loving husband and the wealth I am used to. Countess Vivianna de Blauville, from the series Rich and Poor
